author: USA TODAY, Savannah Behrmann, USA TODAY
title: Protests draw thousands over state stay-at-home orders during coronavirus pandemic
description: Multiple states have seen protests as stay-a-home orders meant to curb the spread of the coronavirus continue.
content:
Thousands of cars jammed streets surrounding Michigan's state capitol in protest of Gov. Gretchen Whitmer's stay-at-home order.
